###Pure
Class simple::model::Person
{
  firstName: String[1];
  lastName: String[1];
}

###NonRelational
DocumentStore simple::store::MongoDB(
    Collection PERSONS
    (
        firstName String
    )
)

###Pure
function mongo::semiStructured(): TabularDataSet[1]
{
    simple::model::Person.all()->project([
        col(x | $x.firstName, 'First Name')

    ])
}

###Mapping
Mapping simple::mapping::document
(
    simple::model::Person: Pure
    {
        ~src simple::model::Person
        firstName: $src.firstName
    }
)

###Connection
DocumentStoreConnection simple::connection::documentStoreConnection
{
    store: 'meta::external::store::document::tests::object::TestMongoStore';
    type: 'Mongo';
    specification: Static
    {
        name: 'my_mongo';
        host: 'localhost';
        port: 27017;
    };
    auth: Test;
}